title: Week 5 recap
itunes:title: Week 5 recap
description:
A room filled with heroes - Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling, Marc Sessler and Colleen Wolfe – break down each game from Week 5 of the regular season including the Bengals and the Falcons hanging on to undefeated records in overtime, and a thrilling ending to the Sunday night game between the Giants and the 49ers.
